On the vanity, there are various toiletries including soap dispensers, bottles, and a folded white towel. A large mirror is mounted above the vanity, reflecting the opposite side of the room, including an open white door. To the right of the mirror, a smaller circular magnifying mirror is attached to the wall. In the foreground, a white paneled door is partially open, leading into the bathroom. A white bath mat is visible on the floor.
